{"tid":1406031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩 好撚大穫....","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:59:19.000Z","uid":166222,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"88d49773573e722822ee5e4551564fcad45d003a","tid":1406031,"uid":166222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:56:29.000Z","msg":"我知道香港人好有愛 <br />\n有錢就錢 有力就出力 <br />\n但出還出 都要有腦咁出 <br />\n大佬呀 啲劵都要錢買㗎！<br />\n就咁擺係地下 有啲仆街藍絲一手就拎一疊<br />\n一陣要撤嘅時候 物資又拎唔切<br />\n最後放哂係到<br />\n又益哂班狗 搞唔撚掂 <br />\n唔撚再可以咁！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）<span style=\"color: red;\">最好每個區放置街站</span> 等人有秩序咁拎<br />\n<br />\n2）<span style=\"color: red;\">放一啲信任得過嘅鋪頭 </span><br />\n（例如 提供裝備或飲食業個啲地方 <br />\n等手足可以經過上去拎）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記住</span><br />\nGear好重要 物資都好重要！！<br />\n所以我地一定要好好珍惜！<br />\n最後多謝大家嘅付出"},{"pid":"c1177f9e45d2c1d75c4f710687ebdc35295631ac","tid":1406031,"uid":110332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:56:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5AM好開始，今晚早啲瞓！有咩今日買聽日唔準消費！地鐵頭班車就好開始塞！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f816b16fd0847a67afb14891b5126f31619fc17","tid":1406031,"uid":166222,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6OEsZAn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6OEsZAn.png&h=8c74b004&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b22f0bf92d79322f1a0be26ad8f2f08a7cda0189","tid":1406031,"uid":166222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:57:44.000Z","msg":"8.5 全城三罷 <br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d42c2091de688769fe2c40e4465b8cac95cd1ca","tid":1406031,"uid":34293,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />白痴   膠撚過雨傘"},{"